org.openbel.framework.api
Interface SpeciesDialect

All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultSpeciesDialect
public interface SpeciesDialect

SpeciesDialect constrains a kam to a specific species. The species dialect must provide the namespaces that supported the target species.

Author:
Anthony Bargnesi <abargnesi@selventa.com>
